---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title={'About | Essays'} description="About the author">
  <section class="about-page fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-content">
        <p>
          Welcome. This is a space for essays, reflections, and long-form writing on topics 
          that matter to me — technology, design, creativity, and the human experience.
        </p>

        <p>
          I'm a writer and technologist who believes in the power of clear thinking and careful craft. 
          Every piece here is an attempt to work through an idea thoroughly, to understand something 
          better by putting it into words.
        </p>

        <h2>The Writing</h2>

        <p>
          Articles here cover a range of subjects, often at the intersection of technology and culture. 
          Some are practical, sharing lessons learned from building things. Others are more reflective, 
          exploring questions that don't have easy answers.
        </p>

        <p>
          I write slowly and revise often. An essay might take weeks to reach a form I'm satisfied with. 
          This isn't about perfection — it's about taking the time ideas deserve.
        </p>

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

        <p>
          If something here resonated with you, or if you want to discuss an idea, I'd love to hear from you.
          You can find me on <a href="#">Twitter</a> or reach me by <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">email</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: var(--spacing-section) 0;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
